event: content_block_stop
data: {"index":0,"blockType":"text","finalContent":"---\n\n## CI/CD & Project Health Report — Complete Blackout\n\n### Executive Summary\n\n**All 8 GitHub API calls and 3 web search fallbacks returned zero usable data.** The expired GitHub token blocks every CI/CD, issue, and PR query. Project health is **unassessable**.\n\n---\n\n## Tool Execution Matrix\n\n| # | Operation | Repository | Tool | Status |\n|:-:|-----------|------------|------|:------:|\n| 1 | List CI/CD workflows | `openagentic-sdk` | `list_workflows` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 2 | List CI/CD workflows | `oats` | `list_workflows` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 3 | Recent workflow runs | `openagentic-sdk` | `get_workflow_runs` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 4 | Recent workflow runs | `oats` | `get_workflow_runs` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 5 | Open issues | `openagentic-sdk` | `list_issues` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 6 | Open issues | `oats` | `list_issues` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 7 | Open pull requests | `openagentic-sdk` | `list_pull_requests` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 8 | Open pull requests | `oats` | `list_pull_requests` | ❌ Token expired |\n| 9 | Web fallback (sdk) | — | `web_search` | ❌ No results |\n| 10 | Web fallback (oats) | — | `web_search` | ❌ No results |\n| 11 | Broad web fallback | — | `web_search` | ❌ No results |\n\n---\n\n## Your Questions — Answered Honestly\n\n| Question | Answer |\n|----------|--------|\n| **Is CI/CD green?** | ❓ **Unknown** — Cannot reach GitHub Actions API. Zero visibility into workflow definitions, run history, or pass/fail status. |\n| **How many open issues?** | ❓ **Unknown** — `list_issues` blocked for both `openagentic-sdk` and `oats`. |\n| **How many open PRs?** | ❓ **Unknown** — `list_pull_requests` blocked for both repos. |\n| **Overall project health?** | ⛔ **Unassessable** — With no CI/CD, issues, PRs, commits, or branch data, there is zero signal to evaluate project health. |\n\n---\n\n## Cumulative Failure Tally Across Both Sessions\n\nCombining your previous repository analysis request with this CI/CD check:\n\n| Category | Calls Attempted | Succeeded | Failed |\n|----------|:--------------:|:---------:|:------:|\n| **Authentication** | 1 | 0 | 1 |\n| **Repository metadata** | 4 | 0 | 4 |\n| **Branches & commits** | 6 | 0 | 6 |\n| **CI/CD workflows & runs** | 4 | 0 | 4 |\n| **Issues & PRs** | 4 | 0 | 4 |\n| **Web search fallback** | 4 | 1 | 3 |\n| **Total** | **23** | **1** | **22** |\n\n> **4.3% success rate** — the single success was a web search that confirmed the org and repo names exist, but provided no CI/CD or issue data.\n\n---\n\n## Impact Assessment\n\n```diagram\n{\n  \"type\": \"flowchart\",\n  \"title\": \"GitHub Observability — Current State\",\n  \"layout\": \"vertical\",\n  \"nodes\": [\n    {\"id\": \"token\", \"label\": \"⛔ GitHub Token\\nEXPIRED\", \"shape\": \"hexagon\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"cicd\", \"label\": \"CI/CD Pipelines\\nBLIND\", \"shape\": \"rectangle\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"issues\", \"label\": \"Issue Tracker\\nBLIND\", \"shape\": \"rectangle\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"prs\", \"label\": \"Pull Requests\\nBLIND\", \"shape\": \"rectangle\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"commits\", \"label\": \"Commit History\\nBLIND\", \"shape\": \"rectangle\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"risk1\", \"label\": \"Broken builds\\ngo undetected\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"warning\"},\n    {\"id\": \"risk2\", \"label\": \"Critical bugs\\nuntracked\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"warning\"},\n    {\"id\": \"risk3\", \"label\": \"Stale PRs\\nblock releases\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"warning\"},\n    {\"id\": \"risk4\", \"label\": \"Security patches\\nmissed\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"warning\"}\n  ],\n  \"edges\": [\n    {\"source\": \"token\", \"target\": \"cicd\"},\n    {\"source\": \"token\", \"target\": \"issues\"},\n    {\"source\": \"token\", \"target\": \"prs\"},\n    {\"source\": \"token\", \"target\": \"commits\"},\n    {\"source\": \"cicd\", \"target\": \"risk1\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"issues\", \"target\": \"risk2\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"prs\", \"target\": \"risk3\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"commits\", \"target\": \"risk4\", \"style\": \"dashed\"}\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Remediation — Single Blocker, Single Fix\n\n| Priority | Action | Command | Time |\n|:--------:|--------|---------|:----:|\n| **P0** | **Rotate the GitHub PAT** | GitHub → Settings → Developer Settings → Tokens → Generate with scopes: `repo`, `workflow`, `read:org` | 2 min |\n| **P0** | **Inject into MCP proxy** | `kubectl set env deployment/github-mcp GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_NEW -n openagentic` | 1 min |\n| **P0** | **Verify** | Re-run `get_user` — should return your profile | 30 sec |\n\nOnce the token is live, I will instantly re-execute all 19 failed API calls and deliver:\n\n- [ ] **CI/CD status** — workflow names, last 10 runs, pass/fail/duration\n- [ ] **Open issues** — count, labels, assignees, age\n- [ ] **Open PRs** — count, review status, merge readiness\n- [ ] **Commit velocity** — recent activity on main branch\n- [ ] **Project health score** — composite of all signals\n\n> [!CAUTION]\n> **This is audit session #4 with total GitHub blindness.** Every CI/CD, issue, and PR question will continue to return \"unknown\" until the token is rotated. No workaround exists — the MCP proxy rejects all requests pre-flight. **Please escalate PAT rotation as a P0 action item.**"}

